Package com.i2group.apollo.infoservice.transport

Contains classes for the service that provides system-wide information for the Intelligence Analysis Platform.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
DataSourcesAndSchema A container for information about the primary and external data sources that Intelligence Analysis Platform services interact with.
DateTimeValidationResult Contains the result of a request to validate a date and time value.
SecurityLevels Contains the SecurityAccessLevel and SecurityGrantLevel for a particular user on a particular piece of data.
UserLoginInfo The login information for a particular user.
UserSecurityDimensions Contains a set of UserSecurityDimensions for "access" SecurityDimensions, and another set for "grant" SecurityDimensions.
 

Enum Summary
LogLevel Indicates the level at which to log a message.
